id: pm-97yv
title: Document pm-changelog external repo dependency and pad-match fix in RELEASING.md
description: "RELEASING.md documents the automated daily release pipeline but does not mention the critical external pm-changelog repo dependency, the padded-month version matching incident (2026.05.27 vs 2026.5.27), or the pattern for debugging silent release skips. The pm-changelog package is a SEPARATE repo that must be kept in sync — this is not documented anywhere in tracked docs."
type: Chore
status: closed
priority: 2
tags[4]: "area:docs","area:release",debugging,reliability
