updated_at: "2026-06-07T13:43:38.047Z"
author: audit-docs-tests-agent
acceptance_criteria: "- RELEASING.md 'Failure Handling' section has a 'Silent skip debugging' subsection covering:\n- run-release-pipeline.mjs exit reasons (tracker_only_changes, empty_generated_changelog_section)\n- pm-changelog as separate repo; bumping it requires coordinated publish\n- git fetch --tags --force before local changelog regen to avoid tag-drift"
