body: "## Context\nFrom memory session 2026-05-28 (release unblock):\n- 'daily release silently skipped 05-25..27: pm-changelog padded month 2026.05.27 vs pm-cli's unpadded 2026.5.27 match -> exited 0 skipped (green but no release)'\n- 'pm-changelog is maintained as a separate release dependency and must stay coordinated with pm-cli release logic'\n- 'same-day -N = semver prerelease'\n- 'git fetch --tags --force + regenerate before checking CHANGELOG drift locally'\n\nRELEASING.md sections 'Automated Daily Driver' and 'Failure Handling' do not mention:\n1. pm-changelog is a separate npm package in a separate repo\n2. How to debug silent skips (check run-release-pipeline.mjs exit reason)\n3. The padded-month version matching gotcha\n4. The git fetch --tags --force requirement before local changelog regen\n\n## Acceptance criteria\n- RELEASING.md 'Failure Handling' section has a 'Silent skip debugging' subsection covering:\n  - run-release-pipeline.mjs exit reasons (tracker_only_changes, empty_generated_changelog_section)\n  - pm-changelog as separate repo; bumping it requires coordinated publish\n  - git fetch --tags --force before local changelog regen to avoid tag-drift\n\n## Evidence\ndocs/RELEASING.md lines 200-206 (failure handling); memory note 2026-05-28 release unblock"
